net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data

Class MutableCellTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.AbstractTableModel
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.MutableCellTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TableModel

    public class MutableCellTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel
    Implements a TableModel using a List of List objects. Use the setValueAt() method to populate the model. The row and and column count will be increased as necessary. To fine tune the model you may also set the column name and/or class using the setColumnName() and setColumnClass() methods.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
